Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_top_cell(25.10)                                      init_top_cell(25.10)

Name
       init_top_cell

Syntax
         init_top_cell <top_cell_name>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies  the  name of the top module. This variable is used only when
       reading Verilog netlist information. It replaces the  previous  rda_In-
       put(ui_topcell) configuration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies TOP as the top cell in the de-
                sign.

                set init_top_cell {TOP}

Related Information
              * init_design

